"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Juli 11, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104rja1665702608398.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/rja1665702608398.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/rja1665702608398.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"rja1665702608398\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      $textexist\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"rja1665702608398___textexist_292341\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Return an indication of whether the specified message or help text exists.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"rja1665702608398__topic_d90152e1_d90153e1_d90154e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rja1665702608398__p_d90155e1_d90156e1_d90157e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$textexist</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">(</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">IDString</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">)</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"rja1665702608398__topic_d59997e1_d59998e1_d59999e1_d60000e1_d60001e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d525607e75\">\n                       \n Parameters\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"rja1665702608398__table_d9803e1_d9804e1_d9805e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Parameters</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"rja1665702608398__table_d9803e1_d9804e1_d9805e1__entry__1\">\n Parameter\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"rja1665702608398__table_d9803e1_d9804e1_d9805e1__entry__2\">\n Data Type\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"rja1665702608398__table_d9803e1_d9804e1_d9805e1__entry__3\">\n Description\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rja1665702608398__table_d9803e1_d9804e1_d9805e1__entry__1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">IDString</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rja1665702608398__table_d9803e1_d9804e1_d9805e1__entry__2\">\n String\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rja1665702608398__table_d9803e1_d9804e1_d9805e1__entry__3\">\n Identifier of the message or help text\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"rja1665702608398__topic_d60002e1_d60003e1_d60004e1_d60005e1_d60006e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d525607e129\">\n                       \n Return Values\n </h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"rja1665702608398__li_d35750e1_d35751e1_d35752e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">1</code>, if the message or help text identified by <var class=\"keyword varname\">IDString</var> exists.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"rja1665702608398__li_d35753e1_d35754e1_d35755e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">0</code>, otherwise.\n </li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"rja1665702608398__topic_d60007e1_d60008e1_d60009e1_d60010e1_d60011e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d525607e153\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rja1665702608398__d5916e20\">Allowed in all component types.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"rja1665702608398__topic_d60012e1_d60013e1_d60014e1_d60015e1_d60016e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d525607e163\">\n                       \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rja1665702608398__p_d90173e1_d90174e1_d90175e1\">The <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$textexist</span> function indicates whether the message or help text specified by <var class=\"keyword varname\">IDString</var> can be found in UAR files containing <span class=\"ph filepath\">/msg/*.msg</span> files. It is commonly used to determine if a message or help text exists before trying to display it on a form, but it can be used in a report or service as well.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rja1665702608398__p_d90176e1_d90177e1_d90178e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$textexist</span> uses the current language and library (in <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$language</span> and <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$variation</span>) to retrieve the text. If a message or help text cannot be found with the current <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$language</span> and <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$variation</span>, Uniface also looks for combinations with language USA and library USYS.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"rja1665702608398__section_fnt_qjj_1cc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d525607e199\">Example: Initializing a Static Label Field</h2>\n<div class=\"div\">\n<p class=\"p\">In the following example, the function <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$textexist</span>\n               is used to initialize a static label field, ensuring that the 8006 message does not\n               appear in the label:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"rja1665702608398__pre_ccg_rjj_1cc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">; initialize labels only when message exists\nif ($textexist(\"%%$componentname%%%.LAB1\"))\n LAB1/init = $text(\"%%$componentname%%%.LAB1\")\nelse ; label not found, use default\n LAB1/init = \"Default Label\"\nendif\n</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xtf1665702608323.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$text</a><p>Return the text of a message or help text.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531624\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531624\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "$textexist Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Juli 11, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 $textexist Return an indication of whether the specified message or help text exists. $textexist ( IDString ) Parameters Table 1. Parameters Parameter Data Type Description IDString String Identifier of the message or help text Return Values 1 , if the message or help text identified by IDString exists. 0 , otherwise. Use Allowed in all component types. Description The $textexist function indicates whether the message or help text specified by IDString can be found in UAR files containing /msg/*.msg files. It is commonly used to determine if a message or help text exists before trying to display it on a form, but it can be used in a report or service as well. $textexist uses the current language and library (in $language and $variation ) to retrieve the text. If a message or help text cannot be found with the current $language and $variation , Uniface also looks for combinations with language USA and library USYS. Example: Initializing a Static Label Field In the following example, the function $textexist is used to initialize a static label field, ensuring that the 8006 message does not appear in the label: ; initialize labels only when message exists if ($textexist(\"%%$componentname%%%.LAB1\")) LAB1/init = $text(\"%%$componentname%%%.LAB1\") else ; label not found, use default LAB1/init = \"Default Label\" endif Copy Related Links $text Return the text of a message or help text. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}